      • equals

        public static <T> boolean equals(T o1,
                                 T o2)
        Checks for equality for objects of any type. Either or both arguments may be null.
        类型参数:
        T - Generic object class type
        参数:
        o1 - First object to compare
        o2 - Second object to compare
        返回:
        the result of equals() if both objects are non-null, or true if both objects are null, or false if one object is null and the other is non-null.

      • getAnonymizedText

        public static java.lang.String getAnonymizedText(java.lang.String text)
        Method used to mask info in logs. All characters other than first and last will be replaced by "*".
        参数:
        text - to be masked
        返回:
        anonymized text. Returns the input value for null or empty strings.

      • getDelimitedString

        public static java.lang.String getDelimitedString(java.lang.String[] array,
                                                  java.lang.String delimiter)
        Returns a string value with array elements separated by the delimiter character.
        参数:

        delimiter - Delimiter character to separate elements of the array
        返回:
        String value with array elements separated by the delimiter character.
